{
  "stem": "9963.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on top of that as I mentioned it, what we could take a bath.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Every day when you get up before you go to work, before you take your piece of bread that you can go in the washroom to wash up like a human being.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because as far I was concerned, to me, that was a much more improvement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I know that I had no choice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But for crying out loud, to-- people taken to work, not to give them any the possibility to keep it clean.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But you have to the-- at night with the flies, with the fleas would eat you alive, but you had to go out from the barracks and to sleep outside.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And many times I slept outside in the other camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In the middle night, the rains came on you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You practically drowned because you slept in the air, weather comes with the mountains and you-- you wake up, you know that you're in the flood of water.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But here we didn't have to do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So that that is already an improvement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At this camp, again we're-- we're cutting wood, you know, the trees away to make room for the different roads, to put down different roads over there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- it was also very hard work, but it was-- you know, the foremen were a little bit more lenient.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could talk to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could bribe them, and do some things in that camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How I bribed them, with money, usually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Money talks everywhere, and I had to steal money from home because the home was still-- you know, even my parents were already living in another house.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But still I could take money from home.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
